extends page-layout
include mixins/analyzer-info
include mixins/conditional-access-code-fix-remark

block content

    h1.page-header BH1008 - HttpResponseRedirect
    .row
        .col-sm-12
            p.lead
                | Access to <code>Redirect</code> method of <code>System.Web.HttpResponse</code> or <code>System.Web.HttpResponseBase</code>

            +analyzer-info('BH1008', 'HttpResponseRedirectAnalyzer')


    //.row
    //    .col-sm-12
    //        h2 Motivation
    //        p TBD

    .row
        .col-sm-12
            h2 Code Fixes
            p
                | Multiple code fixes will be presented. The diagnosed nodes will be replaced with one of:
                ul
                    li
                        code URLHelper.Redirect()
                    li
                        code URLHelper.LocalRedirect()


            p Before:
            pre
                | Response.Redirect("https://google.com");

            p After:
            pre
                | using CMS.Helpers;
                | ...
                | URLHelper.Redirect("https://google.com");
                | // or
                | URLHelper.LocalRedirect("https://google.com");

            +conditional-access-code-fix-remark()


